    "body": "Commit Message:​​\r\nThe `get_swizzle_mode` function sets the swizzle mode for output tensors but hardcodes the element size to 2 (fp16). However, in `wgrad_gemm_fp8_fp8_fp32_nt`, the output tensor is fp32 (element size 4), causing incorrect swizzle mode selection.\r\n\r\n​​Fix:​​\r\nAdded an is_fp32_out parameter to dynamically determine the element size (2 for fp16, 4 for fp32).",
    "created_at": "2025-06-17T08:56:07Z",
